        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks FCD for information, which will make him "strike out a good deal".</p>
            <p>Has received German pamphlet.</p> 
<p>Will read work by John Soelberg Wells [? <hi rend="italic">A treatise on the diseases of the eye</hi> (1869, 1870)].</p> 
            <p>Discusses his work on expression.</p>
